{"tid":984989,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣幫一個有抑鬱症嘅朋友","createTime":"2019-01-17T08:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T05:26:50.000Z","uid":83490,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"947c88456d7eb4c7db8bbcb5868b5121eb8631d9","tid":984989,"uid":83490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:51:01.000Z","msg":"呢幾日特登約佢食飯先知原來佢有depression <br />\n食飯同佢傾計嘅時候都感覺到佢好唔開心<br />\n佢好似人生無左目標咁<br />\n佢又好似無乜朋友 成日都無野做<br />\n好驚佢亂諗野<br />\n聽到呢個消息搞到我自己心情都有小小低落<br />\n呢排仲有唔小事煩緊<br />\n我又唔係好識開解佢 好驚講錯說話令佢更唔開心<br />\n所以都一直煩惱除左約佢多啲出黎食飯之外有咩幫到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw佢已經有睇醫生同食藥 但係好似無乜用咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f58c44bb7d5a87c92ecf3de2a71ef9c9c254d0e","tid":984989,"uid":148332,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T09:09:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6Ta4Z2ks7Tc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6Ta4Z2ks7Tc&d=b1OF%2B0C98ImIiU9%2BlqVqRu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=79f1a45b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6Ta4Z2ks7Tc</a><br />\n比佢聽"},{"pid":"7b686aaf7f6aeec2e8cd4c4c2f89c92d2444fd14","tid":984989,"uid":2772,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T09:10:37.000Z","msg":"出少句聲 唔該你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada71b4dc5bff1f0f3af8d7e07c7aa3b78832483","tid":984989,"uid":83490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b686aaf7f6aeec2e8cd4c4c2f89c92d2444fd14","tid":984989,"uid":2772,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T09:10:37.000Z","msg":"出少句聲 唔該你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係唔搵佢傾下計又驚佢亂諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\